Subject: [RESEND PATCH v4 1/4] dt-bindings: thermal: k3: Add VTM bindings documentation
Date:   Wed, 18 Mar 2020 14:00:25 +0530
Message-ID: <20200318083028.9984-2-j-keerthy@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.17.1
